data.description: Check out this amazing updated home in sought after Western Hills subdivision!  With 3 spacious bedrooms and 2  bathrooms this home boast tons of natural lighting, luxurious porcelain tile flooring, granite counter tops and stainless appliances in the kitchen.  Two captivating living spaces gives the new owners an abundant space to entertain guest.  Impeccable location just minutes form major shopping, golf, Temple ISD schools, and I-35.  This home will not last long!  Seller is licensed Real Estate Agent.
